4. Configuration and Theming
The default configuration is located at /etc/xdg/swaync/config.json. To customize it without root access: 
Create your local config folder: mkdir -p ~/.config/swaync.
Copy the default files:
cp /etc/xdg/swaync/config.json ~/.config/swaync/config.json
cp /etc/xdg/swaync/style.css ~/.config/swaync/style.css.
Edit the files: Modify style.css to change the look (colors, fonts, transparency) and config.json to change behavior (position, button actions). 
