5. Essential Commands
You can interact with SwayNC via the terminal to test your setup: 
Open/Toggle the Control Center: swaync-client -t -sw
Reload Config (after editing CSS/JSON): swaync-client -rs
Clear All Notifications: swaync-client -C
Test a Notification: notify-send "Hello World" "This is a test notification". 
